{{Han etyl}}
The character {{lang|zh|七}} was originally a pictogram of a vertical line and a horizontal line bisecting each other – original character of {{och-l|切|to cut}}.

The top-most horizontal stroke is done from left to right. The vertical line and bottom-most horizontal line are done as one stroke, from top-left to bottom-right.

{{zh-hanzi}}

